profile:
Over 25 years experience in Property Maintenance, Landscaping, and Snow Plowing for both Commercial & Residential.
Serving the Mississauga, Oakville, Etobicoke, and Milton Area.
Lawn maintenance packages starting at only $25.
Contact us for a free quote and ask us about our MTB360 Package!

Services Include:
Mowing / Edging - Pruning/Hedging  Weed Control - Fertilization  Mulching 
Power blowing grass and leaves 
Waste Removal - Weekly or BiWeekly Service
Fall Clean-Ups, Spring Clean-Ups 
Mulching - Eavestrough Cleaning and replacement/installation 
Ask us about our landscaping services 
Interlock/driveway sealing 
Retaining Walls (design, creation, light installation, etc.) 
Planting/Transplanting 
Garden bed installation 
Sod/seed lawns 
Weed control 
Over seeding 
Snow plowing/snow removal
